-------------------------------Server Folder Structure -----------------------------------------

db_conn (folder):
Manages database connections. This is an essential folder for database connectivity. (IMPORTANT FOLDER)

routes (folder):
Holds all route handlers that define how the server processes requests.

model (folder):
Stores database schema and table creation scripts.

server.js:
The core of the backend. This file initializes the server, sets up middleware, connects to the database, and handles incoming requests.

DB.txt:
Stores the database username and password.
